{"tid":918654,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【最緊要開心】前TVB綠葉王轉行做保安 揚言收入好過做藝人","createTime":"2018-11-27T11:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T05:15:32.000Z","uid":24160,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b2087a8b0d24f1c3f9c4bae6d3a99880c4835a","tid":918654,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181127/large/1543305376_60f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F1543305376_60f6.jpg&h=8d54a1be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n昔日經常演法官嘅綠葉王高俊文，原來已轉行做保安。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181127/large/1543305377_acc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F1543305377_acc9.jpg&h=c0d3da34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n13年效力王維基嘅港視。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181127/large/1543305379_3ab4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F1543305379_3ab4.jpg&h=926c63ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同鄧萃雯拍《巾幗梟雄之義海豪情》。（劇照）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181127/large/1543305379_99c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F1543305379_99c5.jpg&h=01d1e92b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同李楓拍HKTV《大眾情性》。（劇照）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181127/large/1543305378_e22d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F1543305378_e22d.jpg&h=aaa622d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n13年高俊文（左起）同郭鋒、陸駿光及張松枝喺政總外上演撐港視嘅《半澤直樹》短劇。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181127/large/1543305380_f899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F1543305380_f899.jpg&h=6487cb4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高俊文喺《怒火街頭2》做法官。（網上截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181127/large/1543305382_331a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181127%2Flarge%2F1543305382_331a.jpg&h=c8c9beff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高俊文早年接受訪問講電視辛酸。（資料圖片）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n今年8月剛踏入60歲嘅「綠葉王」高俊文，當年經常喺無綫劇集做專業人士角色，13年佢加盟王維基旗下嘅香港電視網絡（HKTV），點知因為政府唔發牌，令好多電視人包括高俊文在內加入失業大軍行列。<br />\n<br />\n原來高俊文好似李中寧一樣，已經轉咗行做保安，今日有周刊登咗高俊文喺一間連鎖百貨公司做保安嘅相，高俊文接受訪問時，話現時收入穩定，好過以前做藝人，又話自己唔會再拍番嘢。所謂行行出狀元，最緊要活得開心同健康。《蘋果》曾多次聯絡高俊文，但未獲回覆。至於早年同高俊文過檔港視嘅張松枝，對高俊文轉行一事話唔清楚：「佢都轉咗行，我都唔方便講啲乜嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n高俊文係78年無綫第7期藝員訓練班出身，同甘國衛及已故嘅鄺佐輝係同屆畢業生，喺無綫經常扮演專業人仕，例如《學警出更》做教授、《通天幹探》、《怒火街頭》及《律政新人王》做法官等等，又同鄧萃雯拍過《巾幗梟雄之義海豪情》等劇。<br />\n<br />\n13年高俊文過檔港視，因為港視不獲發牌，佢同成班港視員工連續兩晚喺政總門外抗議，仲同陸駿光、張松枝及郭鋒上演撐港視嘅《半澤直樹》短劇，飾演部長角色。之後佢接受《蘋果》訪問時，自爆70年代因為被指拒接無綫監製王天林通告而無奈離開無綫，到2000年佢再返無綫，又因為拍《楚漢驕雄》墮馬受傷一事同無綫有訴訟，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>後來拍《我的野蠻奶奶》做皇帝，點知第一日開工遇着「阿姐」汪明荃，由於自己唔爭氣成日NG，被阿姐話佢冇做功課，自己同阿姐拗咗幾句之後，第二日就被換角。</ins></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"1488dd06ba588a4d0d56346454f487a7be098c2d","tid":918654,"uid":24160,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/5-09-2015/bLN8HN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F5-09-2015%2FbLN8HN.gif&h=0052c4b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5986622622a240f413e168cbec2bda7a6748615c","tid":918654,"uid":27064,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T11:33:46.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊點解巴打會post佢<br />\n睇到最後先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"